subject: Horse Racing
lead_paragraph: Deweycheatumnhowe extended his unbeaten streak to 10 last night in the Breeders Crown, harness racing’s season-ending championships for 2- and 3-year-olds. At the Meadowlands Racetrack, Deweycheatumnhowe came through on a night that Donato Hanover, Tell All and Always A Virgin each lost.
